welcome_message_body: Welcome to Petaling Jaya, Malaysia! Known for its vibrant food scene, lively night markets, and beautiful parks, we invite you to explore and enjoy the charm of our city. We hope you have a wonderful time during your visit.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Sultan Abdul Aziz Shah Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Skypark Terminal
terminals.description: The Skypark Terminal at Sultan Abdul Aziz Shah Airport serves primarily domestic flights and is home to Firefly Airlines.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Kuala Lumpur International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The satellite terminal at Kuala Lumpur International Airport serves primarily international flights.

wifi.note: WiFi is available throughout the airport, but may have limited coverage in some areas.
